title: Look Up There's Starlight
overview: A tragic accident turns the life of young woman upside down. Revolving in the world of high fashion, the story follows an innocent Cinderella who is reborn as a domineering CEO. Xue Qi Luo once thought that she had the perfect love, yet she lost everything in a fire on the day of her boyfriend Lu Zhi Yao's engagement to his fiancee. Three years later, Xue Qi Luo returns as Qin Shu, the president of a company entering into the Chinese market for haute couture. With the Lu Group being a strong opponent, Qin Shu finds her way back into Lu Zhi Tao's life.
